creator: TAG corporation
descriptionHtml:
FishingTAG is an application for fishing

You can share fishing points for various fish species. You can also analyze tide based on wether information. You can run fishing challenges with anglers from all over the world and get awards.
If you get more famous in application you can earn a special point that allow you to purchase useful in-app products.
You can also edit pictures for a special anglers. If you post on FishingTAG, it would automatically be posted on designated your SNS accounts

Function in FishingTAG

1. Social
- FishingTAG is similar to blog or SNS, but special as it automatically generates 8 useful information for fishing by taking just one picture
- You can post your thought as an expert on FishingTAG. This allows you to make more friends.
- Unique emoticons and Brand stickers that make your picture more special are available
- By using meta data in the picture, you can share your own fishing point and tide.
- You can share the location with your friends on FishingTAG and then easily go to fishing together
- You can share video channels from other service with your friends

2. Online Fishing competition
- FishingTAG Online Fishing Competition got a patent and will be proceeded different ways
- Hot time fishing competition does not require a big size of fish to win, but your distinctive skills and luck
- Diverse fishing competition will occur in special zones spread all over the area and a special award is waiting for the conqueror of each zone. It has incomparable value to other awards in FishingTAG

3. Measuring the size
- You can measure the size of fish by using a special measure designed by FishingTAG
- By taking just one picture, you can measure the size of fish and 10 useful information for fishing automatically generated
- You can also post high resolution pictures to show your friends

4. Fishing Point
- You will never fail if you check the point before you go to fishing
- Please check fishing points depending on various fish species and each point’s information
- You can be a special angler having a number of followers by sharing your own fishing points

5. Weather and Tide
- Weather and tide are necessary environment information to be checked before fishing. You can easily check on FishingTAG
- FishingTAG will provide you with all necessary and useful information for fishing based on big data
- FishingTAG will provide check-up list depending on weather and tide.

6. Sharing on other SNS
- If you post your picture on FishingTAG, you can easily share it on other SNS(Facebook, Instagram)
- Special picture editing function designed for anglers will make your post outstanding.

7. Guinness
- Challenge yourself to be the best
- Guinness is a special record existing in FishingTAG and will be provided in different ways
- One who has the best record will get compensated in every cycle
- One who has the best record will draw more intention from more users and will earn a special award

8. Review Event
- We welcome Early Adapter. Please use the newest product from out supporter first and leave a review
- You can review a fishing point or a boat.
- More review target will be provided

9. Sharing event
- Please share on-going event. This makes our service more vibrant
- We will randomly select winners and ship a announced gift
